n/author-jozQdQhvGPbtQ0MGa6lrMw">Hạ Hoàn Thuần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/S%E1%BA%AFc-t%E1%BB%A9-T%C3%BA-Phong-t%E1%BB%B1-bi/poem-xxLxY7z4rcP4cV-gZh2gaw">Sắc tứ Tú Phong tự bi - 敕賜秀峰寺碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Nguy%C3%AAn-Tr%E1%BB%ABng/author-_vSGbKXOej4AgRYmpqgykw">Hồ Nguyên Trừng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/T%E1%BA%A1p-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-eQq-ZMWyGeFY-eRWiRKWOQ">Tạp thi kỳ 1 - 雜詩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Trinh/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-m8buZGd9acbui1906QmgWA">Thanh Tâm tài nhân tập tự - 青心才人詩集序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-M%E1%BA%A1nh-Trinh/author-ZpBj6D9P3q-U3JR36g_w5g">Chu Mạnh Trinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Huy-Li%E1%BB%85n/Th%C3%A1t-S%C6%A1n-C%E1%BB%91-Ch%E1%BB%A7-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem--fNwnQGBLSTaiXGQnzBzOQ">Thát Sơn Cố Chủ miếu - 獺山故主廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Huy-Li%E1%BB%85n/author-aojK5yt7X8rTWmkDYWXgEg">Trần Huy Liễn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
